descript.abstract: View of the parcels layer for use with public web applications. This layer has a subset of the attributes that are available in the Parcels layer.
descript.purpose: To provide a parcel data layer that has only those attributes that can be distributed to the general public. This layer will be exported for download files and will be used in web mapping applications that are exposed to the Internet.
